#: enginescript-site-optimizer.php:420
msgid "Use preconnect for domains that host critical, frequently used resources, like Google Fonts. This hint tells the browser to establish a connection (including DNS lookup, TCP handshake, and TLS negotiation) as soon as possible, which can save 100–500ms on the subsequent request. Enter one HTTPS domain per line (e.g., https://fonts.googleapis.com). Only clean domains are allowed - no file paths, query parameters, or fragments."
msgstr ""

